text.section:
A contact lens prescription shall include the following:
The ophthalmic information necessary to accurately fabricate or dispense the lenses including the lens manufacturer, lens series, and the lens material if applicable;
Power and base curve;
Name, license number, telephone number, and for written orders, the signature of the prescribing optometrist, osteopath, or physician;
Patient's name and address, expiration date of the prescription, and number of refills or lenses permitted; and
The date of issuance.
